title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Sep 14 2022
description:
It's outrageous! FBI seizes Mike Lindell's cellphone. Biden celebrates Inflation Reduction Act as market tanks because of inflation. Biden wears sunglasses, gets angry for no reason during speech, can't say "United States of America." Buck says Biden wears those sunglasses so public can't see his eyes reading the teleprompter. Clay agrees and says, "Biden looks less old and dementia-ridden if they cover his face with those shades." Fetterman sinks in polls as public learns the dude can't speak. Caller from El Paso sees illegals crossing border as he talks to Clay and Buck.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
